Package com.ibm.fhir.server.rest

Class FHIRRestInteractionVisitorBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.fhir.server.rest.FHIRRestInteractionVisitorBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FHIRRestInteractionVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FHIRRestInteractionVisitorMeta, FHIRRestInteractionVisitorPersist, FHIRRestInteractionVisitorReferenceMapping
    public abstract class FHIRRestInteractionVisitorBase
extends Object
implements FHIRRestInteractionVisitor
    Abstract base class of the FHIRRestInteractionVisitor. Manages access to the map managing local references (localRefMap) and the array of response Entry objects (responseBundleEntries).
